ROUND FOUR

00:08:12.040 --> 00:08:13.041
Scissors!

00:08:13.208 --> 00:08:14.918
Scissors! Scissors!

00:08:15.043 --> 00:08:16.712
Scissors! Scissors! Scissors!

00:08:16.753 --> 00:08:20.382
Scissors! Scissors! Scissors!
Scissors! Scissors! Scissors!

00:08:23.552 --> 00:08:25.095
Again!!

00:08:25.387 --> 00:08:26.054
ROUND 22

00:08:26.054 --> 00:08:27.973
ROUND 22 — Hit! Cover! Rock,
paper, — Hit! Cover! Rock, paper,

00:08:27.973 --> 00:08:28.015
ROUND 22

00:08:28.015 --> 00:08:28.098
ROUND 22 — scissors! — scissors!

00:08:28.098 --> 00:08:29.099
— Scissors!
— scissors!

00:08:38.191 --> 00:08:40.193
Brings back memories...

00:08:43.905 --> 00:08:49.286
<i>To bring back that
lively energy to the dojo...</i>

00:08:49.745 --> 00:08:53.457
<i>I'm going to need the power
and strength of youth.</i>

00:08:56.710 --> 00:08:58.336
Wart, he's... 2/

00:09:07.054 --> 00:09:09.264
Such power!

00:09:09.598 --> 00:09:12.309
No fair! You're not allowed to dodge!

00:09:13.185 --> 00:09:14.561
That would've settled it otherwise!

00:09:15.103 --> 00:09:16.938
Those aren't the rules!

00:09:17.064 --> 00:09:17.898
Enough.

00:09:17.939 --> 00:09:18.482
Huh?

00:09:19.775 --> 00:09:21.443
| lost.

00:09:21.985 --> 00:09:24.613
If we'd been fighting for real,
how would it have ended?

00:09:24.946 --> 00:09:26.114
All right then!

00:09:26.281 --> 00:09:28.575
The next hit wins!

00:09:29.076 --> 00:09:33.497
You fool. I have no intention of engaging
in mortal combat with you.

00:09:33.663 --> 00:09:34.331
Huh?

00:09:34.372 --> 00:09:36.249
What about the meat?

00:09:36.541 --> 00:09:38.668
| was always going to give it to you.

00:09:38.710 --> 00:09:39.461
Huh?

00:09:39.711 --> 00:09:41.880
So what'd you think?

00:09:41.922 --> 00:09:44.341
Maybe you understand now
that you've had a match.

00:09:44.716 --> 00:09:46.259
Especially you, Saitama.

00:09:46.301 --> 00:09:49.513
Before you knew it,
you were enjoying the competition.

00:09:49.805 --> 00:09:52.390
Otherwise, you wouldn't
have gotten so serious.

00:09:53.141 --> 00:09:54.810
— You listen too, Charanko.
—Yes.

00:09:55.310 --> 00:09:57.437
Martial arts is appealing
in this way,

00:09:57.479 --> 00:10:00.482
a way that you can never get
from merely fighting.

00:10:00.816 --> 00:10:03.652
It's true, Master was getting serious...

00:10:04.152 --> 00:10:07.489
Exactly. That is the essence
of martial arts.

00:10:08.281 --> 00:10:09.574
Bang-sensei!

00:10:09.825 --> 00:10:10.992
Well?

00:10:11.034 --> 00:10:13.829
Perhaps you're now interested
in attending my dojo?

00:10:13.995 --> 00:10:15.038
Nah...

00:10:15.455 --> 00:10:16.456
Not at all.

00:10:20.961 --> 00:10:22.879
Oh, really?

00:10:24.214 --> 00:10:27.592
Whatever, let's go
one more round and finish this!

00:10:27.759 --> 00:10:29.970
Master, shall I play you
next round?

00:10:30.178 --> 00:10:31.513
What? Why?

00:10:35.183 --> 00:10:36.309
(Ah, that's the way)

00:10:39.020 --> 00:10:40.063
(Ah, let's go)

00:10:45.610 --> 00:10:47.904
(Ah, that's the way,
that's the way)

00:10:48.238 --> 00:10:49.739
"My name is Saitama.

00:10:50.198 --> 00:10:53.034
I'm just a guy
who's a hero for fun,

00:10:53.076 --> 00:10:55.412
and I can beat
all the evils of this world. "

00:10:55.495 --> 00:10:59.416
Never miss a day of training

00:10:59.541 --> 00:11:03.420
<i>No air conditioning was pretty hard</i>

00:11:03.461 --> 00:11:06.965
But I was finally rewarded
with this fist

00:11:07.048 --> 00:11:11.178
Of overwhelming power

00:11:11.303 --> 00:11:14.764
Things you can't forget,
like garbage day

00:11:14.848 --> 00:11:19.144
And sale day at the supermarket

00:11:19.227 --> 00:11:21.146
(Ah, cheap, cheap, cheap, cheap)

00:11:21.229 --> 00:11:24.608
Come on, seaweed,
make my hair grow

00:11:24.649 --> 00:11:29.487
One-Punch Folk Song

00:11:29.571 --> 00:11:32.282
I can't stand guys
who are long-winded.

00:11:32.908 --> 00:11:36.995
<i>Shorten it to 20 words or less
and get back to me!”</i>

00:11:45.128 --> 00:11:46.630
(Ah, that's the way,
that's the way)

00:11:46.713 --> 00:11:50.133
One attack, one kill, ONE PUNCH

00:11:50.217 --> 00:11:54.638
One-Punch Folk Song

